column1: (Samsung Galaxy S20 Ultra) The document: "Raport privind Strategia Nationala Anticoruptie pe anul 2019" does not have the images properly placed
column28:
The document mentioned in the summary did not have its images placed properly.

*Preconditions*

* A personal computer with at least Windows 10 Home is used for testing, with the Google Chrome browser installed on it, along with a set of peripherals and a monitor.
* The presence must be made on the main page of the website: [https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.|https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.]

*Reproduction steps*

* Access the main page of [https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.|https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.]
* Press the "F12" key on the keyboard on the surface on which it is placed, and look for the "Dimensions" option (approximately in the middle of the screen).
* Press "Dimensions", and from the list of options displayed, select: Samsung Galaxy S20 Ultra.
* Then, look for the "RUTI according to SNA" menu.
* Identify the section: "Annual reports".
* Press the left mouse button on the surface on which it is placed, the click being positioned on the section: "Annual Reports".
* Then, press the left mouse button on the surface on which it is placed, the click being positioned on the document: "Report on the National Anti-Corruption Strategy for 2019".
* Check the placement of the images in the document.

*Expected results*

* The images in the document are placed properly.

*Current results*

* The images in the document are not placed properly.

column112: RUTI conform SNA-leftsidebar (present on the left side of the page)

column1: (Microsoft Edge) The "Ministerul Dezvoltării Regionale și Turismului" button, in the "Link-uri Utile" menu, does not redirect the end user to the expected website
column28:
The button mentioned in the summary does not lead the end user to the expected website, but to: [http://www.mdlpl.ro/.|http://www.mdlpl.ro/.|smart-link] 

*Preconditions*

* A personal computer with at least Windows 10 Home is used for testing, with the Microsoft Edge browser installed on it, along with a set of peripherals and a monitor.
* The presence must be achieved on the main page of the website: [https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.|https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.]

*Reproduction steps*

* Access the main page of [https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.|https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.]
* Then, look for the "Link-uri utile" menu/sidebar (on the right side).
* Identify the button: "Ministerul Dezvoltării Regionale și Turismului".
* Press the left mouse button on the surface on which it is placed, the click being positioned on the "Ministerul Dezvoltării Regionale și Turismului" button.

*Expected Results*

* The button redirects the end user to the expected website.

*Actual Results*

* The end user is not directed to the expected website.
